{"tid":2492963,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（圖文分析）到底摩佬係真回塘定係熱刺批中後防廢","createTime":"2021-04-17T13:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T19:30:00.000Z","uid":1275,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2e629fb49678f061f80fa9aa09c1f965789f3b46","tid":2492963,"uid":1275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"首先，我諗以我呢個user name講下佢係咪回塘應該有啲參考價值掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多，直接入正題，以下係一啲熱刺今季失波嘅截圖，因為我認為今季熱刺出事主要係防守上嘅出事，而防守亦都係摩連奴一直嘅專長，我主要將呢啲失波分為四個主因<br />\n<br />\n1.防守唔夠緊密/空位太多<br />\n摩連奴曾經係sky sports講過佢要求佢執教嘅球隊防守要夠compact，但似乎今季熱刺好多嘅失波正正就係因為防守唔夠緊密所引起嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWxTopBw2fDRe2gY2CHp2QTJvABiscsVxj25AEremu7ME?filename=yxxjOSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxxjOSi.jpg&h=8a87f48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢球咁就算禁區內有6個人都好請問點解中間會有一大個空位比根度簡插入嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當然負責man mark根度簡嗰個企係度睇波都值得抵屌啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeKyqESYdNidZ75ufDLnFd5pPPhqMJfP5qz12AXzrDckg?filename=9O6sXNn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9O6sXNn.jpg&h=2fe54004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又例如呢球點解熱刺會無啦啦同紐卡素成4v4嘅情況，而中間會有成條私家路比人地球員行入去嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeM1EvjLtyGASaDtbcKd6xHhnQ3euWbQPKtQAUEuiJAs7?filename=55AYj1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F55AYj1Q.jpg&h=aeab6b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張對阿仙奴好明顯見到防中同成條後防線分開到有成個奧迪加特係度，結果咪比佢射入囉<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTd6RnbzgecudMBCaLnFdCxn153dqc7d3uAJhYagmnSpo?filename=GURc8Wy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGURc8Wy.jpg&h=a2113de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張熱刺7個球員對白禮頓3個球員，人數就佔優啦，但睇下有幾多個係企係啲無用嘅位防守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而右邊又有幾多空位比人插入<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX1TLGCKR9miLJoAXPzyXyATJ9iK3wJ5KjMQGtyxKoncT?filename=kN0pZ45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkN0pZ45.jpg&h=2bfd23b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後係呢張新鮮滾熱辣琴晚對愛華頓嘅cap 圖熱刺禁區頂5個對拖肥2個球員，即使係咁其實我哋睇到施古臣係好容易無人看管下跑入去禁區下接應傳中球射入，當然施素高係睇到施古臣嘅插入啦，仲用隻手指向施古臣添，但請問有邊個熱刺球員睇到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論熱刺防守人多定人少，似乎都做唔返摩連奴引以為傲嘅緊密防守，特別係人多嘅時侯，防守球員嘅企位都不能為熱刺帶嚟明顯嘅防守優勢，對方球員依然可以好輕易有射門機會，球員企位呢啲問題，摩連奴當然責無傍貸啦。<br />\n<br />\n2.比人走身後/插盲眼位<br />\n對住啲球員走身後，熱刺嘅球員好似後知後覺咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb5X6529Dm1DiH3bGEhJDULaHMkL13JDG7WB8JjDqMSKq?filename=Bqvp0f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqvp0f7.jpg&h=6fdc7410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSN3WXEqLvci92ahY2a4NMahevomFNoNNMH2PWxkXZ16N?filename=A94urV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA94urV8.jpg&h=346293c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如呢球文尼cut inside，兩個負責mark文尼嘅熱刺球員明明睇到人地準備斬比文尼都仲可以比文尼跑咗5、6個身位先開始追，特別係利物浦呢招cut inside都出曬名咁濟，摩連奴有無比足防守指示去應付呢啲情況呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQj11V9kKZrRSpjhTU25sHQnu2jXeTjWp9crwaToQfevd?filename=9MpqKLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9MpqKLW.jpg&h=b06604a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如上星期曼聯對熱刺，卡雲尼瘋狂走Dier身後，連熱區即討都睇到呢個問題嘅發生，但摩連奴同佢嘅教練團似乎對呢個問題無反應咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmatn9H8qByAhGKwmWzxha4oozNPtUPzkXBCo3HKewyKLf?filename=tXcf68g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtXcf68g.jpg&h=3873b70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢球仲好笑，韋斯咸有兩個球員準備起動，綠圈條撚樣又係掛住指，屌你老母撚有人睇到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.閘位收縮<br />\n唔知點解比摩佬教/教過嘅球隊都咁鍾意玩閘位收縮，其實對住肯拉邊/推閘位上前嘅球隊真係好輸蝕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmeti3y9YLdFNfX1LqfDVKSBaZw7DxZ9bLWPLRYCwPSany?filename=VCMc9jY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCMc9jY.jpg&h=fa08c594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n例如呢球列古朗收得咁入比阿諾成條私家路插入禁區，結果執雞成功<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUaz8k5x8cGtLh2fwYokokijpMbZHdVT7pwoD21abV4q7?filename=wcd7dNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwcd7dNa.jpg&h=913dce9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如呢球如果阿仙奴斬遠柱嘅話saka基本上又可以有個肥雞餐食，無錯，列古朗又收咗入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心唔知呢個係摩老要求，定球員慣性動作，但even係曼聯前幾季都成日有呢啲情況發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.習慣領先後便死守<br />\n呢個係摩連奴嘅死性就眾所周知啦，但亦都係近年摩佬不論係熱曼都成日臨天光賴尿嘅原因。特別係而家啲弱隊係角球/罰球上都有特別練習部署過，你縮後嚟打其實就係變相為對方送多啲罰球角球，然後比人入波追平。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：做唔到自己所講嘅緊密防守，賽前部署/臨場應變又好似做到pat屎咁，又繼續堅持自己嘅閘位收縮同埋領先後死守，唔話你回塘都唔得啦。"},{"pid":"ee73df8e60bb9b65408aabf0bf48cd7d3fe0aa1d","tid":2492963,"uid":43861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"幫人答<br />\n廢囉on9"},{"pid":"3729eb22bc477a07799a6a5fb6d281d1d9934426","tid":2492963,"uid":99700,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:38:23.000Z","msg":"好少見咁認真嘅分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feee97019e6d176367a3b1a63f8385ef5797e790","tid":2492963,"uid":1275,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"當然，熱刺嘅後防又係咪無辜呢，咁又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家可以欣賞下以下嘅截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQUD4h4Jb3BENofdVK6z55o8Gy7M3Bvs94kwbQNeFBbhY?filename=dceKf8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdceKf8m.jpg&h=3490245e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYA2RyqKYhCfh3QxkhtRek2reJWsTgq4dAck6TdE5zAab?filename=Qpeuse0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpeuse0.jpg&h=e48dae13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母係到收步唔撚跑埋落去掛住係到睇波結過咪比沖入去嘅其中一個紐卡素球員執雞成功囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdNPSneDedPRYFesHaVw3rVwCcH32KsK9ehi7SfPR99qY?filename=T1jaV9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1jaV9v.jpg&h=be6e11f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如呢球屌你老母舉乜撚嘢手呀，有VAR架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbNmyi42vBpPv1XEztvRBXth5EYT9AMmB88bHgdM8NTAv?filename=LGzBRJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGzBRJb.jpg&h=dac6f466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXc9vKECWhyvTJBEgqnaEHZzrh4AdHujsbqjEjU3DKvWM?filename=3ihowJa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ihowJa.jpg&h=a575ca54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個禮拜對曼呢球仲撚離譜，3個球員一齊舉手，有兩個本來同fred平排嘅掛撚住舉手唔撚追結果咪比fred射入囉，屌你有var架<br />\n<br />\n再加埋一系列嘅老烏，熱刺嘅後防都係鳩鳩地架啦，同摩佬嘅責任37開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31cca43f44916d8a18fd6281e12e3143483df38","tid":2492963,"uid":1275,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ee73df8e60bb9b65408aabf0bf48cd7d3fe0aa1d","tid":2492963,"uid":43861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"幫人答<br />\n廢囉on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"廢都要解釋點樣廢法架<br />\n正如阿叔都有講球波係點樣靚法，如果唔係咁做要應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95fa5f59a6854dc211