0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:50:23.000Z","msg":"緊密呀<br />\n個個位都有人嫁<br />\n不過一齊睇漏之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6b6939fb8581264055f0673566afbd3ec9c042","tid":2492963,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheerleading.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0352699c105cc672d862811acb1ce1a8e6a1cebe","tid":2492963,"uid":1275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ad72a4a074f270e0ec1562086e35a1da7004d7a","tid":2492963,"uid":19126,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"都幾有心，不過摩狗果套收縮防守+靠人多既防守技倆已經俾人睇穿哂<br />\n<br />\n以前都話可能俾人屈第二點、-6波、12碼、高波屈死<br />\n<br />\n依家直頭係咁俾人中出任射<br />\n<br />\n當然球員本身係有問題，但今時今日足球已經係好進取+多元化，唔再係以前咁442鳩斬咁單調，但摩連奴根本自己仲活緊係2009年前後，你睇同佢差唔多年紀果D都落哂二線教啦，智利工程師、肥賓、安76、大菲呢D<br />\n<br />\n佢一係進步，一係就落二線教把啦，教大會真係唔再岩佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:05:24.000Z","msg":"企位有問題嘅話根本人多/人少都會有空位比人起腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb146efeb7bc8e9eab890947a9bc27174708941","tid":2492963,"uid":369322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee73df8e60bb9b65408aabf0bf48cd7d3fe0aa1d","tid":2492963,"uid":43861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"幫人答<br />\n廢囉on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"101cb6d3c85a38c1f4a24d64dac7c3506bea0a6f","tid":2492963,"uid":23699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T14:16:16.000Z","msg":"廢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中堅 ：<br />\ndier 舉手王<br />\n黑山 黑人但唔識用身位踢波<br />\ntoby 高波廢<br />\n<br />\n右閘：<br />\n 三叔成日上腦 <br />\n杜生更加唔好提<br />\n<br />\n左閘叫好少少"},{"pid":"16761625ccdf846bc5db84d230eacb4ed9e40dc9","tid":2492963,"uid":172190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"101cb6d3