Z","msg":"雖然冇睇但都幫推！"},{"pid":"d5a68219af497d45b99a86ebcbba9726911a3747","tid":2492963,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feee97019e6d176367a3b1a63f8385ef5797e790","tid":2492963,"uid":1275,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"當然，熱刺嘅後防又係咪無辜呢，咁又唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家可以欣賞下以下嘅截圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dceKf8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdceKf8m.jpg&h=3490245e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qpeuse0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpeuse0.jpg&h=e48dae13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母係到收步唔撚跑埋落去掛住係到睇波結過咪比沖入去嘅其中一個紐卡素球員執雞成功囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1jaV9v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1jaV9v.jpg&h=be6e11f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又例如呢球屌你老母舉乜撚嘢手呀，有VAR架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGzBRJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGzBRJb.jpg&h=dac6f466&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ihowJa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ihowJa.jpg&h=a575ca54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上個禮拜對曼呢球仲撚離譜，3個球員一齊舉手，有兩個本來同fred平排嘅掛撚住舉手唔撚追結果咪比fred射入囉，屌你有var架<br />\n<br />\n再加埋一系列嘅老烏，熱刺嘅後防都係鳩鳩地架啦，同摩佬嘅責任37開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T18:41:29.000Z","msg":"學界水準，企定定舉手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01b9f7e0d93c596e6e1532475b65bddc5113b21","tid":2492963,"uid":4609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite